  [2]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/Queue.html
  [3]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/PriorityQueue.html
  [4]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/LinkedList.html
  [5]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/Queue.html#offer-E-
  [6]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/Queue.html#peek--

